{"TopicId":127939,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"[Not a challenge] Why are so many bad challenges arising?","CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-15T23:22:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-15T23:22:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRecently (since the forum update or so), I\u0027ve been noticing a whole bunch of challenges that look like they were made by someone who never once read the submission guidelines or even put much thought into what other players would\u0027ve already done or could do. Are the forums rapidly growing or what?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nF.E. Make a 1000-part spaceplane!\u003Cbr\u003E\nor\u003Cbr\u003E\nCrash two planes in mid-air!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWith little or no further explanation.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhy are these sorts of things getting posted more than usual?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-15T23:31:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[Not an Attempt]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile these challenges pop up every once in a while, they usually don\u0027t get much attention, being forgotten in the \u0022Second Page of Death\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T00:10:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it has anything to do with the forums. We\u0027re in the doldrums between versions and people are just getting bored.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hobbes Novakoff","CreatedById":129018,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T00:20:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324228\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450224631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it has anything to do with the forums. We\u0027re in the doldrums between versions and people are just getting bored.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis. I used to think about KSP every hour of the day. Now, thanks to a combination of other games\u00A0and a few things currently taking up a lot of my thoughts at the moment, I only really think about it when I\u0027m on the forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kokanee","CreatedById":93886,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T00:23:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr maybe it\u0027s because KSP is TOO popular now. Before, it was only your hardcore space nerd who knew about KSP. Now every truck driving heehaw seems to play it. Newer players are watering down the gene pool so to speak. Death to the newcomers! Protect KSC!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caithloki","CreatedById":139470,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T00:37:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree, I have been wanting to do more challenge videos, but with all these challenges that have been cropping up, most not worth the trouble, I have decided to wait till new year to do more.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoSlash27","CreatedById":111526,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T01:03:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s just a result of new players wanting to participate in the community. Nothing wrong with that. Good challenges get participation and bad challenges get quickly forgotten.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBest,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Slashy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sanic","CreatedById":149920,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T01:36:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324247\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450225416\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002293886\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kokanee\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kokanee said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDeath to the newcomers! Protect KSC!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEasy now \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceplaneAddict","CreatedById":149322,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T01:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m hoping the Dres Awareness thread isn\u0027t in that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, lemme bounce an idea off you people. What would you guys think of a new Better Stock Craft challenge, with our new parts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sanic","CreatedById":149920,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T01:44:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324354\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450230188\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149322\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpaceplaneAddict\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, SpaceplaneAddict said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m hoping the Dres Awareness thread isn\u0027t in that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNonsense! Dres Awareness is something that needed to be done, yet nobody cared enough to try.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T01:48:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324166\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450221774\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pds314\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Pds314 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCrash two planes in mid-air!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003EI\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Elike\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E*ahem* how you just insulted\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:18px;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:none;background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154972-viridian-air/\u0026amp;do=h