excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-16T02:46:39Z\u0022 title=\u002212/16/2015 02:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 16, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Der Anfang\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sanic","CreatedById":149920,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T02:50:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324465\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450233970\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022134627\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Der Anfang\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Der Anfang said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m in the process of a Dres Mission. Although it\u0027s probably mediocre at best... Anyhow, I\u0027m definitely giving it a try.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it\u0027s special in some way, or not \u0027The Martian: Dres Edition\u0027 I\u0027m sure it will be fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mister Dilsby","CreatedById":232743,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T02:52:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuch challenges are a great opportunity to welcome new users, gently point them to the Guidelines, and constructively suggest ways to improve the challenge \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-16T04:16:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222324477\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221450234358\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022111501\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kuzzter\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kuzzter said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuch challenges are a great opportunity to welcome new users, gently point them to the Guidelines, and constructively suggest ways to improve the challenge \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat this guy said.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}